      "groupIds": [],
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "PMR result (r96)\nbatch, 200 iters/req\n\nstd::allocator:\n  p50  8.66 µs\n  p99 15.29 µs\n\nstd::pmr:\n  p50  4.08 µs\n  p99  5.61 µs\n  2.12× faster\n\n(serve mode: no\nwin — see §7)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top"
    },
